name: SSF5
title: Site-Specific Factor 5
subtitle: Malignant Ascites
notes:
**Note 1:**  Record the volume of malignant ascites in milliliters (ml).

**Note 2:**  For an estimated volume, record the estimated value. For an uncertain volume, record the approximate value. 
* For example, volume of malignant ascites is less than 500 ml, record as 500 ml
